# Rastorizer

This project uses Xilinx Vivado to build FPGA designs in batch mode.

## Building the Project

To build the project, run the following command in your terminal:

```sh
vivado -mode batch -source build.tcl -log build/vivado.log -journal build/vivado.jou
```

To flash the project, run the following command in your terminal:

```sh
vivado -mode batch -source flash.tcl -log build/vivado.log -journal build/vivado.jou
```

## VGA simulator

You need the following tools to use the simulator:
```sh
sudo apt install verilator libsdl2-dev
```
To run it:
```sh
cd sim
make clean // Optional
make
./vga_sim
```
